---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import { social } from '../data/social';
---

<Base title="About" activePage="about" description="Purple Directive builds compliance-grade software and operations infrastructure for clinical research. Meet the team behind the work.">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="about-hero">
    <p class="about-tagline">About Us</p>
    <h1>We Build What Clinical Research<br/>Operations Actually Need</h1>
    <p class="about-subtitle">
      Purple Directive is a consultancy that builds compliance-grade software and
      operations infrastructure for sponsors, CROs, and research sites. We work at
      the intersection of clinical research and technology — where regulatory rigor
      meets modern engineering.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- Origin story — split -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="about-split">
      <div class="about-split-left">
        <h2>How We Got Here</h2>
        <p>
          We started where a lot of small CROs start — running active studies with
          borrowed SOPs, manual tracking, and tools designed for organizations ten
          times our size.
        </p>
        <p>
          The commercial platforms were either too expensive or too rigid. So we started
          building: SOPs aligned to ICH E6(R2/R3), a clinical trial management system
          with a real audit trail, automation for the repetitive work that burns out
          coordinators. Each tool was built because we needed it ourselves.
        </p>
        <p>
          Then we realized other sites needed the same things. That's when Purple
          Directive became a product company, not just an internal tooling effort.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-split-right">
        <div class="milestone-stack">
          <div class="milestone">
            <span class="milestone-marker"></span>
            <div>
              <strong>Clinical Operations</strong>
              <span>Phase I-IV study coordination, regulatory submissions, site start-up</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="milestone">
            <span class="milestone-marker"></span>
            <div>
              <strong>SOP Library</strong>
              <span>12 SOPs covering the full study lifecycle, aligned to current ICH guidelines</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="milestone">
            <span class="milestone-marker"></span>
            <div>
              <strong>CTMS Development</strong>
              <span>Multi-tenant trial management system with 21 CFR Part 11 compliance</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="milestone">
            <span class="milestone-marker"></span>
            <div>
              <strong>AI-Augmented Operations</strong>
              <span>Multi-agent system for document generation, study intelligence, and compliance automation</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Founders -->
  <section class="section section-tinted">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>The Team</h2>
      <p>Two co-founders. One builds the operations. The other builds the systems.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="founders-grid">
      <div class="founder-card">
        <div class="founder-avatar avatar-tyrian">🐌</div>
        <h3>Tyrian M.</h3>
        <span class="founder-role">Co-Founder</span>
        <p>
          Clinical research operations, regulatory compliance, and the business side
          of making research sites audit-ready. Background in GCP, ICH E6, and the
          daily reality of running studies with small teams and real deadlines.
        </p>
        <div class="founder-domains">
          <span>Clinical Ops</span>
          <span>Regulatory</span>
          <span>Business</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="founder-card">
        <div class="founder-avatar avatar-violet">🔮</div>
        <h3>Violet M.</h3>
        <span class="founder-role">Co-Founder</span>
        <p>
          AI architecture, infrastructure engineering, and compliance-grade software
          development. Designed the multi-agent system, built the CTMS, and handles
          everything that compiles, deploys, or runs inference.
        </p>
        <div class="founder-domains">
          <span>Engineering</span>
          <span>AI Systems</span>
          <span>Infrastructure</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Principles -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>How We Work</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="principles-grid">
      <div class="principle-card">
        <div class="principle-num">01</div>
        <h3>Build What You Use</h3>
        <p>Every product we sell started as an internal tool. The SOP bundle is the same library we use on our own studies. The CTMS runs our own operations. We don't build things we haven't tested on ourselves first.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="principle-card">
        <div class="principle-num">02</div>
        <h3>Compliance Is Infrastructure</h3>
        <p>Regulatory compliance isn't a checkbox at the end. It's the foundation everything else is built on. Our software has audit trails, our SOPs reference current ICH guidelines, and our operations are inspection-ready by default.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="principle-card">
        <div class="principle-num">03</div>
        <h3>Small Teams, Real Problems</h3>
        <p>We build for organizations running 1-10 studies with lean teams — not 500-person CROs with dedicated IT departments. Our tools are sized for the people who actually need them.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="principle-card">
        <div class="principle-num">04</div>
        <h3>Ship, Then Improve</h3>
        <p>We'd rather deliver a working tool this week than a perfect tool next quarter. Every product we release gets better based on real use, real monitoring visits, and real feedback from coordinators in the field.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Connect -->
  <section class="section section-deep">
    <div class="connect-layout">
      <div>
        <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
        <p>Whether you're looking for compliance infrastructure, custom software, or just want to follow along as we build — here's where to find us.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="connect-links">
        <a href="/hire" class="connect-card">
          <span class="connect-icon">&#128172;</span>
          <strong>Work With Us</strong>
          <span>Consulting, software, partnerships</span>
        </a>
        <a href={social.linkedin.url} target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="connect-card">
          <span class="connect-icon">&#128188;</span>
          <strong>LinkedIn</strong>
          <span>{social.linkedin.handle}</span>
        </a>
        <a href={social.x.url} target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="connect-card">
          <span class="connect-icon">&#128172;</span>
          <strong>X / Twitter</strong>
          <span>{social.x.handle}</span>
        </a>
        <a href={social.github.url} target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="connect-card">
          <span class="connect-icon">&#128187;</span>
          <strong>GitHub</strong>
          <span>{social.github.handle}</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  /* Hero */
  .about-hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: var(--spacing-xl) var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .about-tagline {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--purple-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .about-hero h1 {
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .about-subtitle {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* Origin split */
  .about-split {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--spacing-xl);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about-split-left h2 {
    margin-top: 0;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }

  .about-split-left p {
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* Milestone stack */
  .milestone-stack {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--spacing-md);
    border-left: 2px solid var(--purple-primary);
    padding-left: var(--spacing-lg);
  }

  .milestone {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--spacing-sm);
    align-items: flex-start;
    position: relative;
  }

  .milestone-marker {
    width: 10px;
    height: 10px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--purple-primary);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 0.35rem;
    position: absolute;
    left: calc(-1 * var(--spacing-lg) - 6px);
  }

  .milestone strong {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.15rem;
  }

  .milestone span {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* Founders */
  .founders-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--spacing-lg);
  }

  .founder-card {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: var(--spacing-xl);
    text-align: center;
    transition: border-color 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
  }

  .founder-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--purple-primary);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .founder-avatar {
    width: 72px;
    height: 72px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin: 0 auto var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .founder-avatar.avatar-tyrian {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fef3c7, #fde68a);
    border: 3px solid #f59e0b;
  }

  .founder-avatar.avatar-violet {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ede9fe, #ddd6fe);
    border: 3px solid #a78bfa;
  }

  .founder-card h3 {
    margin: 0 0 0.2rem;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }

  .founder-role {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--purple-primary);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  }

  .founder-card p {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.65;
    margin: var(--spacing-md) 0;
  }

  .founder-domains {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .founder-domains span {
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    color: var(--purple-primary);
    background: rgba(91, 33, 182, 0.08);
    padding: 0.25em 0.65em;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  /* Principles */
  .principles-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .principle-card {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: var(--spacing-lg);
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }

  .principle-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--border-hover);
  }

  .principle-num {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--purple-primary);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .principle-card h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin: 0 0 var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .principle-card p {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* Connect */
  .connect-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--spacing-xl);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .connect-layout h2 {
    margin-top: 0;
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }

  .connect-layout > div:first-child p {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  .connect-links {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .connect-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.2rem;
    padding: var(--spacing-md);
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    border-radius: 10px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
  }

  .connect-card:hover {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
  }

  .connect-icon {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
  }

  .connect-card strong {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .connect-card span:last-child {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-hero h1 { font-size: 1.6rem; }

    .about-split {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--spacing-lg);
    }

    .founders-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .principles-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .connect-layout {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--spacing-lg);
    }

    .connect-links {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
